title.narrative: Africa Leadership Training and Capacity Building Program (Africa Lead)
Formation au commandement de l'Afrique et programme de construction de capacité (avance de l'Afrique)

description.narrative: USAID a édité ce champ selon les exceptions décrites dans le transparent d'aide étrangère et la Loi de responsabilité de 2016.

Working across public and private institutions, Africa Lead is building capacity among Africas emerging food security leaders to devise and manage their country investment plans. We operate across sub-Sahara Africa with hubs in Kenya and Ghana.
